activities.name: Move Data from Synapse to Snowflake DIMSALESPERSON

sqlReaderQuery.value:
select * from INZADBA.DIMSALESPERSON
WHERE ETL_UPDATE_DATE >= CONVERT(datetime,'@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}')
AND ETL_UPDATE_DATE < CONVERT(datetime,'@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}')
